   "source": [
    "{\n",
    " \"cells\": [\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"markdown\",\"metadata\":{},\"source\":[\"# Invoice Field Extractor\\n\",\"**NLP Project 23 of 100**\\n\",\"\\n\",\"## Project Overview\\n\",\"Extract structured fields (invoice number, vendor, date, total amount) from raw invoice text using regex patterns and spaCy NER.\\n\",\"\\n\",\"## Learning Objectives\\n\",\"1. Combine regex and NER for information extraction.\\n\",\"2. Handle semi-structured document formats.\\n\",\"3. Validate extraction quality with field-level metrics.\\n\",\"\\n\",\"## Problem Statement\\n\",\"Given raw invoice text, extract key fields into a structured format. This automates manual data entry.\\n\",\"\\n\",\"## Why This Matters\\n\",\"- AP teams process thousands of invoices manually.\\n\",\"- Extraction errors cause payment delays and reconciliation issues.\\n\",\"- Automating extraction saves significant labor and reduces errors.\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"markdown\",\"metadata\":{},\"source\":[\"## Dataset: Synthetic invoices generated for educational purposes.\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"import subprocess, sys, importlib\\nfor pkg in [\\\"pandas\\\",\\\"numpy\\\",\\\"matplotlib\\\",\\\"seaborn\\\",\\\"spacy\\\"]:\\n    try: importlib.import_module(pkg)\\n    except ImportError: subprocess.check_call([sys.executable,\\\"-m\\\",\\\"pip\\\",\\\"install\\\",\\\"-q\\\",pkg])\\ntry:\\n    import spacy; spacy.load('en_core_web_sm')\\nexcept: subprocess.check_call([sys.executable,\\\"-m\\\",\\\"spacy\\\",\\\"download\\\",\\\"en_core_web_sm\\\"])\\nprint('Ready.')\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"import numpy as np, pandas as pd, re, spacy\\nimport matplotlib.pyplot as plt, seaborn as sns\\nimport warnings; warnings.filterwarnings('ignore')\\nsns.set_style('whitegrid')\\n%matplotlib inline\\nnlp = spacy.load('en_core_web_sm')\\nSEED = 42; rng = np.random.default_rng(SEED)\\nprint('Loaded.')\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"markdown\",\"metadata\":{},\"source\":[\"## Generate Synthetic Invoices\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"vendors = ['Acme Corp','GlobalTech Inc','Smith & Co','Delta Services','Pacific Supply Ltd']\\ninvoices = []\\nfor i in range(100):\\n    inv_num = f'INV-{rng.integers(10000,99999)}'\\n    vendor = rng.choice(vendors)\\n    date = f'{rng.integers(2024,2026)}-{rng.integers(1,13):02d}-{rng.integers(1,29):02d}'\\n    total = round(rng.uniform(100, 50000), 2)\\n    tax = round(total * 0.08, 2)\\n    text = (f'Invoice Number: {inv_num}\\\\nDate: {date}\\\\nFrom: {vendor}\\\\n'\\n            f'Subtotal: ${total:,.2f}\\\\nTax: ${tax:,.2f}\\\\nTotal Due: ${total+tax:,.2f}\\\\n'\\n            f'Payment Terms: Net 30\\\\nPlease remit payment to {vendor}.')\\n    invoices.append({'text': text, 'true_inv_num': inv_num, 'true_vendor': vendor,\\n                     'true_date': date, 'true_total': round(total+tax, 2)})\\n\\ndf = pd.DataFrame(invoices)\\nprint(f'Generated {len(df)} invoices')\\nprint(df['text'].iloc[0])\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"markdown\",\"metadata\":{},\"source\":[\"## Extraction Functions\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"def extract_invoice_number(text):\\n    m = re.search(r'Invoice\\\\s*(?:Number|No\\\\.?|#)?\\\\s*:?\\\\s*(INV-?\\\\d+)', text, re.IGNORECASE)\\n    return m.group(1) if m else None\\n\\ndef extract_date(text):\\n    m = re.search(r'Date:\\\\s*(\\\\d{4}-\\\\d{2}-\\\\d{2})', text)\\n    return m.group(1) if m else None\\n\\ndef extract_total(text):\\n    m = re.search(r'Total\\\\s*Due:\\\\s*\\\\$([\\\\d,]+\\\\.\\\\d{2})', text)\\n    return float(m.group(1).replace(',','')) if m else None\\n\\ndef extract_vendor(text):\\n    m = re.search(r'From:\\\\s*(.+)', text)\\n    return m.group(1).strip() if m else None\\n\\n# Test on first invoice\\nsample = df['text'].iloc[0]\\nprint(f'Invoice #: {extract_invoice_number(sample)}')\\nprint(f'Date:      {extract_date(sample)}')\\nprint(f'Vendor:    {extract_vendor(sample)}')\\nprint(f'Total:     {extract_total(sample)}')\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"markdown\",\"metadata\":{},\"source\":[\"## Run Extraction on All Invoices\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"df['ext_inv_num'] = df['text'].apply(extract_invoice_number)\\ndf['ext_date'] = df['text'].apply(extract_date)\\ndf['ext_vendor'] = df['text'].apply(extract_vendor)\\ndf['ext_total'] = df['text'].apply(extract_total)\\n\\n# Accuracy per field\\nfor field in ['inv_num','date','vendor','total']:\\n    acc = (df[f'true_{field}'] == df[f'ext_{field}']).mean()\\n    print(f'{field:10s} accuracy: {acc:.1%}')\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"# Visualize extraction accuracy\\nfields = ['inv_num','date','vendor','total']\\naccs = [(df[f'true_{f}'] == df[f'ext_{f}']).mean() for f in fields]\\nplt.figure(figsize=(8,4))\\nplt.bar(fields, accs, color='steelblue', edgecolor='black')\\nplt.title('Field Extraction Accuracy'); plt.ylabel('Accuracy'); plt.ylim(0,1.1)\\nplt.tight_layout(); plt.show()\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"markdown\",\"metadata\":{},\"source\":[\"## Summary\\n\",\"- **Regex-based extraction is highly effective** for structured invoice formats.\\n\",\"- **Near-perfect accuracy** on synthetic data; real invoices vary more.\\n\",\"- **spaCy NER can supplement regex** for entity types like organization names.\\n\",\"- **For production, consider OCR + layout-aware models** (LayoutLM) for scanned invoices.\"]}\n",
    " ],\n",
    " \"metadata\":{\"kernelspec\":{\"display_name\":\"Python 3\",\"language\":\"python\",\"name\":\"python3\"},\"language_info\":{\"name\":\"python\",\"version\":\"3.11.0\"}},\n",
